Title: Semantic Economics Paper Search Engine Backend
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Eduard", "BrÃ¼ll", email = "eduard.bruell@zew.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Backend utilities for a semantic economics paper search engine. 
    Handles syncing RePEc archives, parsing RDF files, generating embeddings, 
    and managing the DuckDB database. Includes a Plumber API for search queries.
